Package org.seed.core.api

Interface StoredProcedureCall

public interface StoredProcedureCall
A StoredProcedureCall represents a call of a stored procedure. If there are any outputs, register output type classes first via awaitOutput
Author:
seed-master

      void awaitOutput(int paramIndex, Class<?> outputClass)
